trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control is used as a container for other controls, especially when controls are generated programmatically.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontrollen skal brukes som en beholder for andre kontroller spesielt når Kontroller genereres programmatisk.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: The PanelDesigner class provides design-time support for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> controls in a visual designer.
trans-unit.target: Klassen PanelDesigner gir støtte for utforming for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>Kontroller i en visuelle utformeren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: However, for all new implementations of the Panel control, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner> instead of the PanelDesigner.
trans-unit.target: For alle nye implementeringer av panelet kontrollen, kan du imidlertid bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner>i stedet for PanelDesigner.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning koden kildekode som beskriver de tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> method maps a specified property and value to a specified markup style.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A>metoden tilordner en angitt egenskap og verdi til en angitt markup-stil.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.OnBehaviorAttached%2A> method provides notification when a behavior is attached to the designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.OnBehaviorAttached%2A>metoden varsles når en virkemåte er knyttet til utformeren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.OnBehaviorAttached%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner>klasse når det oppretter den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll eller en kopi av kontrollen på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Maps a specified property and value to a specified markup style.
trans-unit.target: Tilordner en angitt egenskap og verdi til en angitt markup-stil.

trans-unit.source: The MapPropertyToStyle method provides special handling for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A> properties, but calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ReadWriteControlDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> base method for all other values of the `propName` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Metoden MapPropertyToStyle gir spesiell behandling for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A>Egenskaper, men kall av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ReadWriteControlDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A>basere metode for alle verdiene i den `propName` parameteren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ReadWriteControlDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string containing the property name.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder navnet på egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: An object that is the property value.
Provides notification when a behavior is attached to the designer.
trans-unit.target: Varsles når en virkemåte er knyttet til designer.

trans-unit.source: The OnBehaviorAttached method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ReadWriteControlDesigner.OnBehaviorAttached%2A> base method.

Then the OnBehaviorAttached maps the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A> properties to the appropriate style by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> method, if these properties are defined.
trans-unit.target: Deretter OnBehaviorAttached tilordner den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A>Egenskaper for riktig stil ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A>metoden hvis disse egenskapene er definert.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A>
